# GitLab MR Description

Use the shared skill at {{HOME}}/.ai-skills/gitlab-mr-description/SKILL.md.

When triggered, read that file and {{HOME}}/.ai-skills/gitlab-mr-description/template.md, then use `glab` first (`glab mr view`, `glab mr diff`, `glab mr note list`, and `glab api` when needed) to draft a paste-ready GitLab MR description from verified MR, diff, commit, issue, and local code context.
